news.title: Dream11’s co-founder buys apartment for Rs 138 crore in Malabar Hill
news.para: The transaction for this super-premium apartment spread over a carpet area of 9,546 sq ft is valued at Rs 1.45 lakh per sq ft, making it one of the most expensive property deals in the country based on the per sq ft rate.

news.title: Los Angeles rental hits $40,000 per month as fires disrupt housing market
news.para: Incoming calls at LA Estate Rentals, which manages and leases homes in some of the area’s costliest neighbourhoods, have jumped to 500 a day, more than 10 times the number before the fires, said owner Patrick Michael.

news.title: UK's Vistry warns of uncertain market conditions
news.para: Vistry, which has issued three profit warnings since last October, reaffirmed its forecast for 2024 adjusted pre-tax profit at about 250 million pounds ($305.1 million).

news.title: House prices in UK rise by most since February 2023
news.para: Average house prices rose by 3.3% in the 12 months to November - the fastest increase since February 2023 - after a downwardly revised 3.0% increase in October, the Office for National Statistics said.

news.title: India's infra-driven economy will lead to CAGR growth of 7-8% in cement demand: Report
news.para: The report stated that after a brief slowdown anticipated in FY25E, the sector is expected to witness strong growth, driven by positive demand fundamentals and structural changes within the industry.

news.title: Spain's housing shares inch up after government measures
news.para: Shares of Neinor Homes, Aedas Homes, Metrovacesa and Inmocemento all took a hit on Monday after Spanish Prime Minister Pedro Sanchez announced a plan to raise taxes on holiday rentals and set a tax of up to 100% on purchases of houses by non-European Union foreigners living abroad.

news.title: Odisha mines minister helps seize 20 trucks for ferrying sand illegally
news.para: The minister, who was returning from performing rituals at the Nilamadhab temple during the deity's Pushyabhishek, noticed several trucks transporting sand from the Mahanadi river bed.

news.title: UK'S Persimmon sees 2024 profit at top end of market view
news.para: Shares in the FTSE 100 builder rose about 4.5% to 1,104 pence in early trade, lifting the broader housing index , with most of its blue-chip peers gaining around 3%.

news.title: Mohali: Contractor arrested after lintel collapse in under-construction showroom
news.para: Mohali police have arrested the contractor for culpable homicide, and a judicial probe has been assigned to SDM Mohali.

news.title: Kolkata: Illegal four-storey building keels over during corrective work
news.para: Civic officials said Subho Apartment, tilting at a 45-degree angle, would have to be demolished to prevent a catastrophe. KMC began demolition around 6pm.​

news.title: Varanasi development body begins e-auction of plots under Transport Nagar scheme
news.para: In its official press release on Tuesday, VDA stated that the auction process will continue until Feb 6.

news.title: Rural development minister to allocate 8.21 lakh more houses under PMAY-G for Madhya Pradesh
news.para: About Rs 3,726 crore in central assistance has been released to the state so far this fiscal to ensure swift disbursement of the first installment to beneficiaries to start house construction, the ministry said in a statement on Tuesday.

news.title: Eligible families to soon receive 100 sq yard plots: Haryana CM
news.para: The allotment of 100-square-yard plots to eligible individuals would be carried out in phases, said Saini while chairing a review meeting of the housing for all department held at the secretariat here.

news.title: China's Country Garden posts $24.3 billion loss in delayed 2023 results
news.para: Government figures show property sales in China shrank almost 50% over the past three years as the industry reeled from an unprecedented debt crisis that began in 2021.

news.title: Kolkata: BSNL’s 780-cottah property up for sale at Rs 1,900 crore
news.para: The plot at a prime location — at the intersection of AJC Bose Road and Alipore Road — includes a heritage building on 150 cottahs, and overlooks the Royal Calcutta Turf Club and the Maidan greens.

news.title: I-T dept can attach assets under benami law even if actual owner not traced: Authority
news.para: The alleged benami assets case came to the fore after the department raided three Lucknow-based realty groups that had "purchased big land parcels in the Kakori (Lucknow district) area by paying huge amounts of unaccounted cash".

news.title: CBRE acquires remaining 60% stake in Industrious for $400 million
news.para: The company said it will also create a new business segment called Building Operations & Experience, which will integrate its building operations, workplace experience, and property management.

news.title: PE investment in Indian real estate rise 6% to $2.82 billion in April-December 2024: Anarock
news.para: In the April to December FY25, the industrial and logistics sector captured 62% of total investments, significantly surpassing both the office and residential sectors, which attracted 14% and 15%.
